er files</item></change><change n="meta.79057"><date>06.02.2002</date><respStmt><name>HGV</name></respStmt><item>Record created</item></change><change n="meta.79057"><date>13.11.2007</date><respStmt><name>HGV</name></respStmt><item>Record last modified</item></change><change n="meta.79057"><date>2009-03-20</date><respStmt><name>IDP</name></respStmt><item>Crosswalked to EpiDoc XML</item></change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><head lang="en"><date>V/VI spc</date>
<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Myos Hormos</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><div type="textpart" n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>τῷ κυρίῳ μου καὶ τιμιωτάῳ πατρὶ

    <lb n="2"/>ἀββᾶ Ἰωάννης καὶ τῇ εὐγενεστάτῃ

    <lb n="3"/>μου ἀδελφῇ Σαρρα θυγατρὶ τοῦ προγεγραμ-

    <lb n="4"/>μένου Ἰωάννου καὶ Σλαμω <choice><corr>τῇ συμ-

    <lb n="5"/>βίῳ</corr><sic>της συμβιως</sic></choice> σου. πρὸ πάσης ῥήσεως ἀσπάζω

    <lb n="6"/>καὶ προσκυνῶ τὴν ὑμῶν εὐγένειαν

    <lb n="7"/>ἵνα λάβητε παρ᾽ ἐμοῦ Ἀπολλωνίου

    <lb n="8"/>τὴν ἐμὴν προσηγορίαν. μαρτυρεῖ

    <lb n="9"/>μοι ὁ κύριος ὅτι πάνυ ἐλυπήθην περὶ

    <lb n="10"/>τῆς ἁλώσεως τῆς πόλεώς σου καὶ

    <lb n="11"/>πάλιν ἠκούσαμεν ὅτι ὁ δεσπότης θεὸς

    <lb n="12"/>ἔσωσέν σε καὶ πάντας τοὺς διαφέροντάς

    <lb n="13"/>σου. εὔχομαι <expan>παρ<ex cert="high">ὰ</ex></expan> τῷ θεῷ ὅπως καταξιω-

    <lb n="14"/>θῶ τὴν σὴν συντυχίαν πάλιν ἵνα πε<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ρι</unclear>-

    <lb n="15"/>χαρῆ π<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ο</unclear>ιῶ ὅτι πολλὰ προσαγορεύει

    <lb n="16"/>ὑμᾶς ἡ γυνή <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">σ</unclear>ου. θαυμάζω τὴν σὴν

    <lb n="17"/>πατρικὴν διά<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">θεσιν</supplied> <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ὅ</unclear>τι πῶς οὐκ η<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ρ</unclear><gap reason="lost" extent="1" unit="character"/>ω

    <lb n="18"/>θην τὴν <gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="6" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/>ροση<gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="6" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">με</unclear>τα

    <lb n="19"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/>ο<gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/>σ<gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/>χρα<gap reason="lost" extent="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/> παρακαλῶ καὶ

    <lb n="20"/>προσκυνῶ <gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high"> γρ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ά</unclear>ψον μοί τι περὶ τῆς

    <lb n="21"/>ὑ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">γιεί</unclear>ας σου κ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">α</unclear>ὶ οἰκίας σου. ἀσ-

    <lb n="22"/>πάζω πάντας τοὺς ἐν τῷ ἀφρόνῳ

    <lb n="23"/>σου οἴκῳ ἀπὸ μικροῦ ἕως μεγάλου.

    <lb n="24"/><g type="stauros"/> ἐρρῶσθαι ὑμ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ᾶ</unclear>ς εὔχομαι

    <lb n="25"/><choice><corr>ὑγιαίνοντας</corr><sic>υ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">γ</unclear>ι<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">εν</unclear>ον<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τ</unclear>ας</sic></choice> ἐπὶ μήκιστον

    <lb n="26"/>βίον χρόνον. ὁ <expan>κ<ex cert="high">ύριο</ex></expan>ς δια-

    <lb n="27"/>φυλάξῃ ὑμᾶς.
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="28"/><expan>ἐπίδ<ex cert="high">ος</ex></expan> τῷ προσφιλ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">εσ</unclear>τ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ά</unclear>τῳ καὶ <gap reason="illegible" extent="6" unit="character"/> πατρὶ Ἰωάννῃ <expan>π<ex cert="high">αρὰ</ex></expan> Ἀπολλωνίου.

    <lb n="29"/><space extent="unknown" unit="character" dim="horizontal"/> σω<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">κ</unclear>ωτο.</ab></div></div><div n="meta.79057" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.79057" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="401" notAfter="600">V - VI</date></p></div><div n="meta.79057" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Zum Ort vgl. CE 77, 2002, S. 339.</p></div><div n="meta.79057" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">SB</title><biblScope type="volume">22</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">15482</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">79057</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0239</series>; <biblScope type="volume">22</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">15482</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0239;22;15482" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.79057" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><bibl type="illustration" default="NO">IARCE 31, 1994, S. 165, Fig. 7-8</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.79057" type="history" subtype="locations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><placeName type="ancientFindspot" cert="high" full="yes">Abu Sha’ar</placeName></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>